ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectChambre de commerce de Maniwaki - The Maniwaki Chamber of Commerce (Quebec) ** CHANGE OF BOUNDARIES **
PrecisOrder approving the application by la CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DE MANIWAKI - The MANIWAKI CHAMBER OF COMMERCE in Quebec TO CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT from the townships of Bouchette, Messines, Cameron, Kensington, Maniwaki, Egan-Sud, Montcerf, Bois-franc, Aumond including the villages in those townships to Grand-Remous, Bois-franc, Montcerf-Lytton, Aumond, Déléage, Ste-Thérèse de la Gatineau, Egan-Sud, Maniwaki, Messines, Bouchette, Blue-sea, Gracefield, Cayamant, Kazabazua, Denholm, Low and Lac Ste-Marie.
